{"tid":197273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中史試答，求評","createTime":"2017-04-11T19:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T21:51:41.000Z","uid":51241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d6c6e75c795ba1db05a125225fc0311f64ee4f","tid":197273,"uid":51241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:27:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Subject_Information/chist/PP-chist-C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2FDocLibrary%2FHKDSE%2FSubject_Information%2Fchist%2FPP-chist-C.pdf&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=308abe39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/DocLibrary/HKDSE/Subject_Information/chist/PP-chist-C.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nPaper 1 Q2 Part C<br />\n<br />\n若要評價秦始皇和漢武帝，你會貶低秦始皇而讚揚漢武帝嗎？試援引兩人在統治政策方面的史實支持你的看法。(10分）<br />\n<br />\n答：兩個人都已經死左，仲要人去評價？死者為大，積下口德啦<br />\n<br />\n攞唔攞到5**？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902ebe98dd6b7b1798c5ce4651ceafb3eb4b1946","tid":197273,"uid":51241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:27:57.000Z","msg":"利申返：我唔同意要用到抵死呢個咁重字眼，只係睇唔過眼d左膠連去評論一單新聞入面嘅對同錯都唔得，上道德高地上到離曬地"},{"pid":"90f95e322c51b04fc996bf71ba37b8b3115d78c2","tid":197273,"uid":14539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:51:41.000Z","msg":"開左咁耐無人回 橙 我應你"}]}